{"tid":178372,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[春番]有冇人會明知9成伏都會睇AZ監督新作Re:Creators?","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T15:19:14.000Z","uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"566557d0e97d0e378662421157e9689be664bbb1","tid":178372,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"PV:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-gdJpnkdzzE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-gdJpnkdzzE&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=684f70a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-gdJpnkdzzE</a><br />\n不過呢套原作+系列構成(唔會寫三話後走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )係廣江禮威,應該唔會AZ咁亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n故事睇PV應該就係一堆唔同作品既人物黎左現實世界,有部份人決定追斬個作者(因為佢地係入面太慘?)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7ckPIUe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7ckPIUe.jpg&h=0d198b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zUV7ADx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzUV7ADx.jpg&h=e07db855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"828052b8fd470db8e3f30262a0915fef241c0955","tid":178372,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"人物介紹:<br />\n<a href=\"http://recreators.tv/character/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frecreators.tv%2Fcharacter%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3571b1ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://recreators.tv/character/</a><br />\n水篠颯太（水篠颯太，聲：山下大輝）<br />\n平凡的高中生。<br />\n塞蕾西婭&middot;尤比蒂利亞（セレジア・ユピティリア，聲：小松未可子）<br />\n幻想系機器人作品《精靈機想曲Vogel Chevalier》的女主角。<br />\n梅特奧拉&middot;艾斯特萊希（メテオラ・エスターライヒ，聲：水瀨祈）<br />\n開放世界型RPG《追憶的阿瓦肯》中引導主人公的賢者。<br />\n愛麗絲特莉婭&middot;菲布拉里（アリステリア・フェブラリィ，聲：日笠陽子）<br />\n幻想傳奇漫畫&middot;動畫《緋色的愛麗絲特莉婭》的主人公。<br />\n煌樹真美加（煌樹まみか，聲：村川梨衣）<br />\n幼女向魔法少女動畫《魔法殺手真美加》的主人公。<br />\n彌勒寺優夜（弥勒寺優夜，聲：鈴村健一）<br />\n漫畫《閉鎖區underground-dark night-》的大反派。<br />\n鹿屋瑠偉（鹿屋瑠偉，聲：雨宮天）<br />\n機器人動畫《無限神機Monomagia》的主人公。<br />\n築城院真鑒（築城院真鍳，聲：坂本真綾）<br />\n傳奇系輕小說&middot;動畫《夜窗鬼錄》的登場角色，目的不明的人物。<br />\n布里茨&middot;托卡（ブリッツ・トーカー，聲：斧篤）<br />\n賽博朋克漫畫&middot;動畫《code・Babylon》的登場角色，原本是刑警的賞金獵人。<br />\n軍服公主（軍服の姫君，聲：豐崎愛生）<br />\n現階段被謎團包圍的角色。身穿軍服，華麗地揮舞軍刀。"},{"pid":"336777f4ad6020715c5d36f814b0aec4fd7b7a55","tid":178372,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"聽澤野既曲同班聲優都抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813da45756be01227b063a21c2b73e8e714d4d32","tid":178372,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"小松未可子+坂本真綾=至少睇頭3集"},{"pid":"7a725533f9ef5d1b065c22925ca8a4202b1e8f21","tid":178372,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"唔似az 睇黎把撚啊"},{"pid":"3716e648d191fe67afab437078e96655b02a1365","tid":178372,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔似az 睇黎把撚啊</blockquote><br />\n鹿屋瑠偉（鹿屋瑠偉，聲：<span style=\"color: red;\">雨宮天</span>）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">機器人</span>動畫《無限神機Monomagia》的主人公。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291cfd04752e47d122edbe42a4e15d462dd05527","tid":178372,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"澤神爛片預定"},{"pid":"6a2deee6121a636a069e6a1ef1e00342300afd02","tid":178372,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔似az 睇黎把撚啊</blockquote><br />\n鹿屋瑠偉（鹿屋瑠偉，聲：<span style=\"color: red;\">雨宮天</span>）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">機器人</span>動畫《無限神機Monomagia》的主人公。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我